1
00:00:09,069 --> 00:00:09,865
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,210 --> 00:00:18,838
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,041
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23,717 --> 00:00:26,379
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27,488 --> 00:00:30,116
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:31,825 --> 00:00:34,919
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:35,563 --> 00:00:38,691
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,167 --> 00:00:44,536
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,174 --> 00:00:48,937
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,043 --> 00:00:50,772
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:50,844 --> 00:00:53,176
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54,715 --> 00:00:56,478
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:56,550 --> 00:00:58,450
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:58,519 --> 00:01:00,953
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:02,856 --> 00:01:09,420
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,531 --> 00:01:13,022
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:13,801 --> 00:01:16,668
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,508 --> 00:01:22,805
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,279 --> 00:01:26,803
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:42,807 --> 00:01:45,571
Naruto and others are
out there fighting!

21
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,141
<i>We should be too!</i>

22
00:01:50,715 --> 00:01:56,483
<i>The Weapon Known</i>
<i>as Shinobi</i>

23
00:01:58,290 --> 00:01:58,915
Old man!

24
00:01:59,724 --> 00:02:01,157
Old Man Giichi!

25
00:02:01,226 --> 00:02:02,818
Please open up!

26
00:02:04,229 --> 00:02:05,924
Let's go to the bridge!

27
00:02:06,064 --> 00:02:07,691
If we all do it together,

28
00:02:07,766 --> 00:02:10,098
we can beat Gatô and
his men this time!

29
00:02:15,774 --> 00:02:16,706
Inari...

30
00:02:17,509 --> 00:02:20,239
I made up my mind not
to fight anymore.

31
00:02:21,246 --> 00:02:22,873
Even your father...

32
00:02:24,149 --> 00:02:26,208
The man we called a hero...

33
00:02:27,185 --> 00:02:28,516
He's not with us anymore.

34
00:02:33,658 --> 00:02:37,219
If we were to fight,
many lives would be lost.

35
00:02:38,496 --> 00:02:41,693
I don't want lose something that's
special to me anymore.

36
00:02:42,901 --> 00:02:46,200
No one wants to regret again.

37
00:02:58,483 --> 00:02:59,313
I...

38
00:02:59,718 --> 00:03:01,948
I don't want to regret again, either.

39
00:03:03,321 --> 00:03:05,016
That's why we must fight!

40
00:03:06,391 --> 00:03:09,656
<i>A man should live</i>
<i>his life without regrets.</i>

41
00:03:13,131 --> 00:03:15,224
I love Mommy and Grampa.

42
00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:17,393
And you too, Old Man Giichi!

43
00:03:17,469 --> 00:03:19,460
I love all the people here!

44
00:03:25,844 --> 00:03:27,869
I finally realized...

45
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:31,877
Nothing is accomplished if
I just cry all the time!

46
00:03:32,617 --> 00:03:34,175
I finally got it!

47
00:03:52,537 --> 00:03:57,167
Inari... has grown into
a fine man.

48
00:03:59,644 --> 00:04:03,808
Will you just let Inari go
there by himself?

49
00:04:10,288 --> 00:04:11,152
Open up!

50
00:04:11,289 --> 00:04:12,051
Hey!

51
00:04:13,491 --> 00:04:15,789
I'm asking you to fight with me!

52
00:04:17,262 --> 00:04:19,423
Old man! Please listen to me!

53
00:04:25,737 --> 00:04:26,795
Why...

54
00:04:27,372 --> 00:04:30,102
Why won't anyone open
the door to me?

55
00:04:35,447 --> 00:04:37,074
<i>You are strong!</i>

56
00:04:39,684 --> 00:04:41,174
<i>Naruto...</i>

57
00:05:00,371 --> 00:05:01,497
Zabuza.

58
00:05:01,573 --> 00:05:03,564
You were too full of yourself.

59
00:05:04,442 --> 00:05:06,740
You're too ambitious for your own good.

60
00:05:10,014 --> 00:05:14,075
You assassinated the Mizukage,
but failed to pull off a coup.

61
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:18,080
You left the service with
few men under you,

62
00:05:18,223 --> 00:05:20,157
and became a Rogue Ninja.

63
00:05:20,892 --> 00:05:25,056
Soon after, your name reached
our Hidden Leaf Village.

64
00:05:25,997 --> 00:05:28,090
You needed to raise funds
to strike back.

65
00:05:28,533 --> 00:05:29,898
And you needed to hide

66
00:05:29,968 --> 00:05:31,959
from the Tracking Unit's
pursuit and retaliation.

67
00:05:32,837 --> 00:05:34,429
Isn't that about the reason why

68
00:05:34,506 --> 00:05:37,669
you hired yourself out
to scum like Gatô?

69
00:05:38,977 --> 00:05:39,909
Zabuza...

70
00:05:39,978 --> 00:05:44,039
Do you really believe I've managed
to survive with just Sharingan?

71
00:05:45,650 --> 00:05:49,711
Here's something I didn't copy,
a technique of my own...

72
00:05:51,456 --> 00:05:52,684
to enlighten you!

73
00:06:06,437 --> 00:06:07,301
Lightning Blade!

74
00:06:09,007 --> 00:06:09,837
What the...?!

75
00:06:10,108 --> 00:06:13,100
His hand is...
visibly overflowing with Chakra!

76
00:06:16,247 --> 00:06:18,044
You are too dangerous.

77
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:21,612
Tazuna, the man you are trying
to assassinate,

78
00:06:21,686 --> 00:06:23,244
is the symbol of courage
in this land!

79
00:06:24,155 --> 00:06:27,716
The bridge he is building
is the hope of this land!

80
00:06:28,526 --> 00:06:31,256
And your ambitions will
sacrifice countless lives.

81
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:36,491
That isn't how
a Shinobi is supposed to behave.

82
00:06:37,201 --> 00:06:38,259
Who cares?

83
00:06:40,171 --> 00:06:43,732
I have always fought for
my own ideals.

84
00:06:44,642 --> 00:06:48,271
And that will never ever change!

85
00:06:52,050 --> 00:06:53,574
I'll say it again.

86
00:06:53,952 --> 00:06:54,611
Huh?

87
00:06:55,253 --> 00:06:56,447
Give up.

88
00:07:00,191 --> 00:07:02,751
Your future is... death!

89
00:07:11,569 --> 00:07:12,627
Naruto...

90
00:07:13,204 --> 00:07:14,728
I want you to kill me.

91
00:07:18,176 --> 00:07:19,803
Please, make it quick.

92
00:07:24,682 --> 00:07:27,014
What are you hesitating for?

93
00:07:30,822 --> 00:07:32,414
I just don't get it!

94
00:07:32,824 --> 00:07:37,488
The only reason you are allowed
to live is because you stay strong?

95
00:07:40,832 --> 00:07:43,096
There must be something other
than just fighting...

96
00:07:43,201 --> 00:07:44,361
There must be some other way

97
00:07:44,435 --> 00:07:46,903
for you to make
the others accept you!

98
00:07:48,339 --> 00:07:52,275
Remember when we met at the forest?
Do you know what I thought?

99
00:07:52,343 --> 00:07:54,709
That you and I are much alike.

100
00:07:57,515 --> 00:07:59,244
I'm sure you can relate to me.

101
00:08:01,753 --> 00:08:05,416
I apologize for dirtying
your hands with my blood.

102
00:08:06,691 --> 00:08:07,749
Is that it?

103
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:11,019
Is there really no other way?

104
00:08:13,231 --> 00:08:14,095
No.

105
00:08:18,102 --> 00:08:21,162
If only... we had met under
different circumstances,

106
00:08:21,239 --> 00:08:23,104
we could've been friends.

107
00:08:30,248 --> 00:08:33,843
<i>Please...promise you will</i>
<i>grasp your dream.</i>

108
00:08:35,019 --> 00:08:36,919
<i>He too...</i>

109
00:08:38,189 --> 00:08:41,317
<i>Sasuke also had dreams of his own!</i>

110
00:08:49,834 --> 00:08:53,292
<i>Thank you...</i>
<i>You will become stronger.</i>

111
00:08:55,339 --> 00:08:56,169
Hmm...

112
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:59,141
The super thick fog
has finally begun to clear.

113
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:03,010
There are two over there!

114
00:09:03,281 --> 00:09:04,441
They are facing off each other.

115
00:09:04,515 --> 00:09:05,345
Huh?

116
00:09:06,117 --> 00:09:07,448
I can't see well...

117
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:10,214
Which one is Kakashi Sensei...

118
00:09:11,723 --> 00:09:12,712
One moved!

119
00:09:17,295 --> 00:09:18,023
Huh?

120
00:09:28,339 --> 00:09:30,136
Forgive me, Naruto...

121
00:09:38,282 --> 00:09:40,512
I cannot die yet!

122
00:09:54,699 --> 00:09:55,791
Is this the end...?

123
00:10:11,749 --> 00:10:12,807
What was that?

124
00:11:10,675 --> 00:11:12,165
Zabuza...

125
00:11:15,913 --> 00:11:18,905
Did you say my future
was death?

126
00:11:20,818 --> 00:11:24,811
You're off the mark again, Kakashi!

127
00:11:29,661 --> 00:11:30,491
No...

128
00:11:30,562 --> 00:11:32,120
You're not to go to the bridge alone!

129
00:11:35,367 --> 00:11:38,768
I went all over the town,
but no one wants to come.

130
00:11:39,505 --> 00:11:40,529
I have no choice!

131
00:11:42,441 --> 00:11:43,738
But...

132
00:11:54,787 --> 00:11:58,120
Wait!
You're just a child!

133
00:11:59,258 --> 00:12:04,696
I may be a child, but I already
know what it means to fight.

134
00:12:05,964 --> 00:12:08,296
Because I'm my father's son!

135
00:12:14,306 --> 00:12:15,238
My dear...

136
00:12:18,377 --> 00:12:20,106
Wait a moment, Inari!

137
00:12:29,087 --> 00:12:30,816
Where did he go...?

138
00:12:32,925 --> 00:12:36,861
I didn't notice,
but the fog is starting to lift...

139
00:12:38,330 --> 00:12:40,059
Huh? Is he over there?

140
00:12:43,168 --> 00:12:43,998
Huh?!

141
00:12:55,881 --> 00:12:58,372
What the heck is going on here?!

142
00:13:04,923 --> 00:13:07,084
Isn't that the masked boy?

143
00:13:09,261 --> 00:13:11,957
<i>I didn't expect him to jump in</i>
<i>to save Zabuza...</i>

144
00:13:18,503 --> 00:13:21,802
<i>The boy...is already dead.</i>

145
00:13:26,144 --> 00:13:27,543
You did great, Haku.

146
00:13:34,019 --> 00:13:35,008
Kakashi Sensei!

147
00:13:36,588 --> 00:13:38,613
<i>He intends to slash me</i>
<i>along with the boy?!</i>

148
00:13:39,925 --> 00:13:43,383
That was really a great find I made!

149
00:13:43,929 --> 00:13:45,590
Even in his final moment,

150
00:13:45,664 --> 00:13:48,258
he gave me such
a perfect opportunity!

151
00:13:56,875 --> 00:13:58,672
<i>Haku, bad news.</i>

152
00:14:00,012 --> 00:14:02,913
<i>I have to leave</i>
<i>Land of Water as of tonight.</i>

153
00:14:04,816 --> 00:14:08,946
<i>However, I'll return</i>
<i>to this land someday.</i>

154
00:14:09,655 --> 00:14:11,919
<i>I will rule over this land.</i>

155
00:14:12,791 --> 00:14:14,622
<i>To do that,</i>

156
00:14:14,693 --> 00:14:19,130
<i>what I need isn't consolation,</i>
<i>encouragement or empty words.</i>

157
00:14:20,198 --> 00:14:21,790
<i>What I really need is...</i>

158
00:14:22,067 --> 00:14:23,193
<i>I already know.</i>

159
00:14:23,335 --> 00:14:24,768
<i>You have nothing to fear.</i>

160
00:14:25,137 --> 00:14:27,332
<i>I am your weapon, Zabuza.</i>

161
00:14:27,572 --> 00:14:31,906
<i>Keep me by you as a mere tool</i>
<i>that heeds your every word.</i>

162
00:14:35,113 --> 00:14:36,375
<i>You're a good boy!</i>

163
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:57,298
Haku died and you were
able to move, huh?

164
00:14:59,171 --> 00:15:00,331
I won't forgive you!

165
00:15:00,405 --> 00:15:01,337
Naruto!

166
00:15:01,406 --> 00:15:02,805
You just stay there and watch!

167
00:15:25,364 --> 00:15:26,592
This is...

168
00:15:27,666 --> 00:15:29,293
my battle!

169
00:15:34,506 --> 00:15:35,438
Naruto...

170
00:15:36,708 --> 00:15:39,302
Naruto!
It's good to see you!

171
00:15:41,113 --> 00:15:42,171
<i>Sakura...</i>

172
00:15:43,582 --> 00:15:44,674
Where's Sasuke?

173
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:51,648
Naruto!
Where is Sasuke?

174
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:02,398
Sakura...

175
00:16:03,935 --> 00:16:05,061
Kakashi!

176
00:16:05,337 --> 00:16:07,305
You have no time to take
your eyes off me!

177
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,535
Why don't I go with you?

178
00:16:13,845 --> 00:16:18,043
That way, you won't be going
against your Sensei's word.

179
00:16:19,184 --> 00:16:20,014
Right...

180
00:16:34,299 --> 00:16:35,425
Sasuke...

181
00:16:42,441 --> 00:16:43,465
Huh?!

182
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:12,896
He's cold.

183
00:17:13,505 --> 00:17:16,303
This isn't Genjutsu, is it?

184
00:17:18,743 --> 00:17:21,712
Don't mind me.

185
00:17:22,547 --> 00:17:26,005
This isn't the time to
hold back your emotions...

186
00:17:34,993 --> 00:17:41,023
I-I always got perfect scores
at the Ninja Academy...

187
00:17:42,834 --> 00:17:43,664
Huh?

188
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:48,897
I memorized all the
hundreds of Shinobi rules.

189
00:17:49,541 --> 00:17:52,567
All the tests were a breeze.

190
00:17:53,645 --> 00:17:56,773
Until one day,
this question came up...

191
00:17:59,251 --> 00:18:03,119
State Rule # 25 of
the Ways of the Shinobi...

192
00:18:04,422 --> 00:18:08,654
As always, I simply wrote down
the answer without batting an eye.

193
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:18,035
"A Shinobi must never
show his true feelings

194
00:18:18,103 --> 00:18:19,934
under any circumstances,
no matter what...

195
00:18:21,139 --> 00:18:22,902
The mission always comes first.

196
00:18:23,308 --> 00:18:27,301
A Ninja must have the strength
of character never to shed any tears..."

197
00:18:36,087 --> 00:18:39,682
<i>Is this...how it must be for a Shinobi?</i>

198
00:18:41,693 --> 00:18:43,388
<i>That is so unbearably painful...</i>

199
00:18:45,363 --> 00:18:46,261
Sasuke...

200
00:19:13,825 --> 00:19:17,454
<i>Why...?</i>
<i>Why can't I keep up?</i>

201
00:19:20,465 --> 00:19:21,989
Darn you!

202
00:19:39,351 --> 00:19:40,318
Why you...!

203
00:19:51,296 --> 00:19:54,026
You can't possibly defeat me
the way you are now.

204
00:19:54,532 --> 00:19:55,658
What was that?

205
00:19:56,568 --> 00:20:01,164
You still don't know...
What true strength means!

206
00:20:07,045 --> 00:20:09,479
Let's see how things are going...

207
00:20:16,888 --> 00:20:19,322
Goodbye, Demon!

208
00:20:45,817 --> 00:20:48,479
Both your arms have
now been disabled.

209
00:20:49,988 --> 00:20:51,478
You can't even weave a sign.

210
00:20:55,126 --> 00:20:55,888
Huh?

211
00:21:00,665 --> 00:21:04,192
Oh!
You really got it this time.

212
00:21:07,105 --> 00:21:10,040
You disappoint me, Zabuza.

213
00:22:52,979 --> 00:22:55,072
Huh?! You!

214
00:22:55,314 --> 00:22:57,509
What the heck
are you doing?!

215
00:22:58,151 --> 00:23:00,517
Don't you have anything
to say, Zabuza?!

216
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,153
He was your comrade, right?!

217
00:23:02,355 --> 00:23:05,085
You were always,
always together, weren't you?

218
00:23:05,291 --> 00:23:07,816
He really liked you, you know!

219
00:23:08,261 --> 00:23:13,221
You really don't feel anything?!

220
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:17,164
Next Episode:
"The Demon in the Snow
